title: George Shearing - Interview and Improvisation
description:
Great interview aimed at students of the keyboard.  

From the library LP "Standard School Broadcast" ~ Music Makers ~ Keyboard." 

And educational record from the early 70's in which keyboard players discuss their craft in short interviews that include music improvisations.
